[SN]TITLE[SN]
Boy, 12, charged over 'school bus knife' in Mearns area

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A 12-year-old boy has been charged after allegedly being caught with a knife on a school bus in the Mearns area of Aberdeenshire.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The incident happened at about 15:30 on Monday.
Police Scotland said a report would be sent to the Youth Justice Management Unit.
